Package: kagiPro
Title: Kagi API Client for R
Version: 0.4.1
Description: User-friendly R client for the Kagi APIs (Search, Enrich, Summarizer,
    and FastGPT). Build endpoint-specific query objects, run single or batch
    requests with one reusable connection, and write reproducible JSON outputs
    for analysis pipelines. Includes optional graceful error handling with dummy
    outputs and JSON-to-parquet conversion for downstream workflows.
